{"tid":414309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨報：香港要做東方矽谷","createTime":"2017-09-26T06:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T14:36:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d5b674f3855fa33a8fc22425b81f0615b99351","tid":414309,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170926/s00001/5b0c5da1c58c25054748388b9dd5bdf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F5b0c5da1c58c25054748388b9dd5bdf5.jpg&h=73c3323c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 中共黨媒《人民日報》海外版發表署名文章，指香港要做「東方矽谷」。<br />\n<br />\n文章題為＜發揮自身所長 善用國家支持 香港要做「東方硅谷」＞（編按：港譯「矽谷」），提到「與時並進」是香港必須認真思考的課題，又稱過去十多年香港創科發展相對內地來說是沉寂，原因是「重商社會」及內部政治爭拗，「香港的科研開支約佔GDP的0.73%，而深圳這一數據已經達到了4.05%」。<br />\n<br />\n不過文章指出，香港擁有不少先天優勢，而若香港要在科創發展上「後發先至」，須善用國家支持，「不論是人才交流還是科研基地建設，中央都不遺餘力地給予香港支持」。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，香港想要成為「東方矽谷」，還需要香港社會轉變觀念，用「敢拼敢贏」精神發展創新企業。文章引述香港X科技創新創業平台主席沈南鵬表示，「香港的年輕人創造力強，視野開闊，若能搭建好創業氛圍，這種創新精神會被進一步激發出來」。"},{"pid":"32a39c2b65d9d530e065c16a1d6a77940af6e03f","tid":414309,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00001/1506396135400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F1506396135400&d=hq1Tv1DQFqCq6TPm3S9dwqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=b1520f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170926%2Fs00001%2F1506396135400&h=9fbfe908\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170926/s00001/1506396135400</a>"},{"pid":"791e5209c0c7afdf06e7e9fac6e69f015dfe0f55","tid":414309,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas